usr.gustavo6046.pathman.pathing

Class PathSpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • usr.gustavo6046.pathman.pathing.PathSpace

  • public class PathSpace
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    gustavo6046 The Path Space to which the Plan Space is compiled in order to find the required action plan. It is **recommended** that the Plan Space Manager is used to handle it, instead of accessing it directly! This is strategically equivalent to formulating the plan itself.
